channel.title: Rochester MN
channel.description: I did a post doc at the Mayo Clinic Rochester MN, and while I was there I had a great time playing in The FAiRiEs, playing rubgy with the Rouges, and pretending to be american by driving very large cars. Rochester MN is one of those conservative big small towns in the Midwest where everyone knows each other, and foreigners stick out a mile. So we made sure we did on purpose.
